Star]]''\n|-\n|[[Ryan Boudinot]] || ''[[Blueprints of the Afterlife]]''\n|-\n|[[Keith Brooke]] || ''[[Harmony (Brooke novel)|Harmony]]''\n|-\n|[[Eric Brown (writer)|Eric Brown]] || ''[[Helix Wars]]''\n|-\n|[[Moira Crone]] || ''[[the not yet]]''\n|-\n|[[Nancy Kress]] || ''[[Fountain of Age: Stories]]''\n|-\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"|2013<ref>{{cite news|title=2013 Philip K. Dick Nominees Announced|url=http://www.locusmag.com/News/2014/01/2013-philip-k-dick-nominees-announced/|accessdate=11 January 2014|newspaper=Locus|date=10 January 2014}}</ref> \n|-\n|'''[[Ben H. Winters]]''' || '''''[[Countdown City]]'''''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.philipkdickaward.org/2014/04/2014-philip-k-dick-award-winner-announced.html/ |title=2014 Philip K. Dick Award Announced |work=Philip K. Dick Award press release |date=April 18, 2014 |accessdate=April 19, 2014}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Toh EnJoe]]'' || ''[[Self-Reference Engine]]''\n|-\n|[[Anne Charnock]] || ''[[A Calculated Life]]''\n|-\n|[[Cassandra Rose Clarke]] || ''[[The Mad Scientist\u2019s Daughter]]''\n|-\n|[[Ann Leckie]] || ''[[Ancillary Justice]]''\n|-\n|[[Jack Skillingstead]] || ''[[Life on the Preservation]]''\n|-\n|[[Ian Whates]] (ed.) || ''[[Solaris Rising 2: The New Solaris Books of Science Fiction]]''\n|-\n! colspan=\"2\" align=\"center\"|2014<ref>{{cite news|title=2014 Philip K. Dick Award Nominees Announced|url=http://www.philipkdickaward.org/2015/01/2014-philip-k-dick-award-nominees-announced.html/|accessdate=April 5, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|'''[[Meg Elison]]''' || '''''[[The Book of the Unnamed Midwife]]'''''<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.philipkdickaward.org/2015/04/2015-philip-k-dick-award-winner-announced.html/|title=2015 Philip K. Dick Award Winner Announced|date=April 3, 2014|accessdate=April 5, 2015}}</ref>\n|-\n|''[[Jennifer Marie Brissett]]'' || ''[[Elysium (novel)|Elysium]]''\n|-\n|[[Rod Duncan]] || ''[[The Bullet-Catcher\u2019s Daughter]]''\n|-\n|[[Emmi It\u00e4ranta]] || ''[[Memory of Water]]''\n|-\n|[[