y/article/63523/athenry-twinned-with-newfoundland-town |title=Athenry twinned with Newfoundland town |date=5 September 2013 |work=[[Galway Advertiser]] |access-date=12 June 2017 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170612233007/http://www.advertiser.ie/galway/article/63523/athenry-twinned-with-newfoundland-town |archive-date=12 June 2017 |url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n*[[Ballymoe]] -\n:{{flagicon|USA}}{{flagicon|Nebraska}} [[Boys Town, Nebraska|Boys Town]], [[Nebraska]], United States<ref name=\"US embassy list\">{{cite web |title=Sister Cities |url=https://ie.usembassy.gov/our-relationship/policy-history/sister-cities/ |website=U.S. Embassy in Ireland |accessdate=7 December 2019}}</ref>\n\n*[[Oranmore]] - \n:{{flagicon|France}}{{flagicon|Brittany}} [[Clohars-Fouesnant]], Brittany, France <ref>{{cite news |title=Oranmore twins with Breton village |url=https://www.advertiser.ie/index.php/galway/article/51366/oranmore-twins-with-breton-village |accessdate=7 March 2019 |agency=The Galway Advertiser |publisher=The Galway Advertiser |date=19 April 2012}}</ref>\n\n*[[Tuam]] - \n:{{flagicon|Germany}} [[Straubing, Germany|Straubing]], [[Lower Bavaria]], Germany <ref>{{cite web |title=Tuam - Straubing Twinning |url=http://www.tuam-straubing.ie/ |website=Tuam - Straubing Twinning |accessdate=7 March 2019}}</ref>\n\n===County Leitrim===\n\n===County Mayo===\n\n*[[Ballina, County Mayo|Ballina]] - {{Flagicon|United States}}{{Flagicon|Massachusetts}} [[Pittsfield, Massachusetts|Pittsfield]], [[Massachusetts]], United States<ref name=\"US embassy list\"/>\n\n===County Sligo===\n\n====Sligo Town (borough)====\n\n*[[Sligo]] - {{Flagicon|United States}}{{Flagicon|Florida}} [[Tallahassee, Florida|Tallahassee]], [[Florida]], United States<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://tallahasseeirish.org/?page_id=116|title=The Friends of Sligo Ireland Sponsor Irish Related Events|website=Tallahassee Irish Society|access-date=2018-11-08}}</ref>\n\n==[[Leinster]]==\n\n===County Carlow===\n\n*[[Carlow]]\n