et/site4689/Letham%20has%20been%20twinned%20with%20Monasterboice%20since%202000%20PDF.pdf</ref>\n\n===County Meath===\n*[[County Meath]] -\n:{{flagicon|USA}}{{flagicon|North Carolina}} [[Cary, North Carolina|Cary]], [[North Carolina]], United States<ref name=\"dublin 2016\"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.meath.ie/CountyCouncil/Twinning/ |title=Twinning |website=[[Meath County Council]] |accessdate=4 June 2017}}</ref>\n\n*[[Trim, County Meath|Trim]] -\n:{{flagicon|FRA}}{{flagicon|Eure}} [[\u00c9tr\u00e9pagny]], Normandy, France (1989) <ref name=\"Meath County Council\">{{cite web |url=http://www.meath.ie/CountyCouncil/Twinning/ |title=Twinning |website=[[Meath County Council]] |accessdate=25 June 2017}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.meath.ie/CountyCouncil/MunicipalDistricts/TrimMunicipalDistrict/TrimsTwinnedTown/ |title=Trim's Twinned Town |website=[[Meath County Council]] |accessdate=25 June 2017}}</ref>\n\n*[[Athboy]] -\n:{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Oise|Autonne villages]], Picardy, France (2000) <ref name=\"Meath County Council\"/><ref>{{cite web |url=\nhttp://www.meathchronicle.ie/news/roundup/articles/2011/09/28/4006869-french-twinning-visitors-rendezvous-in-athboy |title=French twinning visitors rendezvous in Athboy |website=[[Meath Chronicle]] |accessdate=25 June 2017}}</ref>\n\n*[[Kells, County Meath|Kells]] -\n:{{flagicon|GBR}}{{flagicon|SCO}} [[Iona]], Scotland, United Kingdom <ref name=\"Meath County Council\"/>\n\n*[[Navan]] -\n:{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Bobbio]], Italy (2002) <ref name=\"Meath County Council\"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.catholicbishops.ie/2002/11/22/freedom-city-bobbio-italy-conferred-cardinal-cahal-daly/ |title=Freedom of the City of Bobbio (Italy) conferred on Cardinal Cahal Daly |website=[[Irish Catholic Bishops' Conference]] |accessdate=25 June 2017}}</ref>\n:{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Broccostella]], Italy (2006) <ref name=\"Meath County Council\"/>\n\n*[[Oldcastle, County Meath|Oldcastle]]\n:{{flagicon|CAN}}{{flagicon|ON}} [[Tecumseh, Ontar